Release:        0
Provides:       locale(desktop-data-SLE:en)
Source0:        uyuni-docs_en.tar.gz
Source1:        uyuni-docs_en-pdf.tar.gz
Source2:        zz-uyuni-docs.conf
BuildRequires:  fdupes
BuildRequires:  filesystem
